" Options initiating with ?m? 
" [global] |'magic'| Set 'magic' patterns ;)
" Examples:
"  \v       \m       \M       \V         matches ~
"  $        $        $        \$         matches end-of-line
"  .        .        \.       \.         matches any character
"  *        *        \*       \*         any number of the previous atom
"  ()       \(\)     \(\)     \(\)       grouping into an atom
"  |        \|       \|       \|         separating alternatives
"  \a       \a       \a       \a         alphabetic character
"  \\       \\       \\       \\         literal backslash
"  \.       \.       .        .          literal dot
"  \{       {        {        {          literal '{'
"  a        a        a        a          literal 'a'
set magic

